速巨变下无法妥协的历史境遇和难以直面的精神创伤。随着老刘的车轮滚滚向前，中国的过去和现在也不断交叉展现。',NULL,NULL,NULL),(NULL,NULL,'The Short Happy Life of Butch Livingston','',2016,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL),('tt3922798','25953430','The Siege of Jadotville','雅多维尔围城战',2016,7.4,3583,7.3,14949,NULL,NULL,'剧情;动作;战争/Action;Drama;Thriller;War','詹米·多南;马克·斯特朗;杰森·奥玛拉/Jamie Dornan;Mark Strong;Emmanuelle Seigner;Jason O\'Mara','里奇·斯迈斯/Richie Smyth','Kevin Brodbin;Declan Power','',NULL,'http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/ipst/public/p2385404115.jpg','http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/spst/public/p2385404115.jpg','http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/lpst/public/p2385404115.jpg'),(NULL,'26772587','The Silk Road','丝绸之路',2016,7.2,164,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'纪录片','Sam Willis','Tim Niel',NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/ipst/public/p2344870132.jpg','http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/spst/public/p2344870132.jpg','http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/lpst/public/p2344870132.jpg'),('tt5191320',NULL,'The Silos',NULL,2016,NULL,NULL,9.1,206,NULL,NULL,'Action;Crime;Drama;Thriller','Jason Beghe;Jon Seda;Sophia Bush;Jesse Lee Soffer','Mark Tinker','Michael Brandt;Derek Haas','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(NULL,'26382787','The Simpsons','辛普森一家 第二十八季',2016,8.9,238,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'喜剧;动画','丹·卡斯泰兰尼塔;朱莉·卡夫娜;南茜·卡特莱特','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/ipst/public/p2270844434.jpg','http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/spst/public/p2270844434.jpg','http://img6.douban.com/view/movie_poster_cover/lpst/public/p2270844434.jpg'),(NULL,NULL,'The Skating Rink','',2016,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL),(NULL,NULL,'The Snow Queen 3: Fire and Ice','冰雪女皇3',2016,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL),('tt5730336',NULL,'The Song of Cotton',NULL,2016,NULL,NULL,5.8,11,NULL,NULL,'Drama;Family','Deshun Wang;Bingyan Yan;Liya Ai','Yuancheng Zh